# Project Agents

This repository exposes custom agent skills in `.claude/agents/`:

- `content-marketer`
- `customer-success-manager`
- `context-manager`

Use these agents when the user requests `/content-marketer`, `/customer-success-manager`, or `/context-manager`, or when the task clearly matches their descriptions.

If Cursor needs a project-visible entry point, keep these skills in `.claude/agents/<agent-name>/SKILL.md` and reference them from this rule.
